org.linqs.psl.model.atom

Class RandomVariableAtom

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.linqs.psl.model.atom.Atom
      • org.linqs.psl.model.atom.GroundAtom
        • org.linqs.psl.model.atom.RandomVariableAtom
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<GroundAtom>, Formula, SummationAtomOrAtom, FunctionTerm

    public class RandomVariableAtom
extends GroundAtom
    A GroundAtom with a truth value which can be modified.

    A GroundAtom is instantiated as a RandomVariableAtom is BOTH of the following conditions are met:

    • it has a StandardPredicate that is open in the Atom's Database
    • it is not persisted in one of its Database's read-only Partitions
